  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "body": "Currently, HostAlias feature [does not support HostNetwork pods](https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/faf4e57f1b9c2ea4671f62c96d4470e4757a3a4e/pkg/api/validation/validation.go#L2062-L2070). This is because HostNetwork pods currently [do not](https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/48b3fb84abdc0fee12299eed262da287d48110de/pkg/kubelet/kubelet_pods.go#L112-L118) have its hosts files managed by kubelet.\r\n\r\nOnce https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/issues/48397 resolves, we can change the validation to make HostAlias also supported by HostNetwork pods.\r\n\r\n/kind feature\r\n/sig node\r\n\r\n@yujuhong @hongchaodeng @thockin ",
